# ---- build artefacts at repo root ----
# probe_/test_ binaries are produced by `make parity-kernels`/`make
# test-kernels`. .cu sources live in dev/cuda/ (and test_gpt2.cu at root).
# The compiled binaries (no extension) and per-binary .log files are not
# tracked. Existing tracked test_* binaries stay tracked until explicitly
# removed (git rm --cached) — gitignore only blocks new additions.
/probe_*
!/probe_*.cu
/probe_*.log
/test_*
!/test_*.cu
!/test_*.py
*.log
